{"tid":2047101,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"史高斯評最強對手：他身高腳長 力量爆滿 能控球 能壓前 能入球","createTime":"2020-06-02T01:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T02:06:22.000Z","uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"379d38a75e0224b09263f0a16f5c44a369a7b8a2","tid":2047101,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:25:45.000Z","msg":"曼聯名宿史高斯日前接受訪問時表示，自己職業生涯中遇過最強的對手，是前阿仙奴隊長韋拉。<br />\n<br />\n「作為一名球員，能夠和韋拉交手，感覺很好。不過要與他比賽，我需要有完全健康的身體，需要很強壯，但我從來不是那一類型的球員，我屬於傳球的那一類。」<br />\n<br />\n「我可以用傳球去擊敗其他球員，但和韋拉比賽太難了。他身高腳長，當你以為你準備拿到皮球時，他一下子就會從你頭頂搶走了。」<br />\n<br />\n「和韋拉比賽很辛苦，但他是個很優秀的球員。他不僅可以控球，也會壓前，亦能夠入球，在比賽中還力量爆滿。」<br />\n<br />\n「每次有人問我，誰是我遇到過的最佳球員時，我會想，對陣韋拉實在棘手。」"},{"pid":"07f58946249ba94e110b23231ebc00a51f5d454d","tid":2047101,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:27:30.000Z","msg":"14吋豬肉條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d925bed44bef3af594fba1dca7d8da2d779c08a","tid":2047101,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"耶耶仲能屈啦"},{"pid":"070f91653cc925dab22e35e1ec81a83f5f7c0085","tid":2047101,"uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d925bed44bef3af594fba1dca7d8da2d779c08a","tid":2047101,"uid":42396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"耶耶仲能屈啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"但韋拉能伸啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i